      <LabelChip text="ROZETKA FULFILLMENT · MULTI-MARKETPLACE GATEWAY" variant="red" />
      <h1 class="rze__h1">A <span class="rze__accent">multi-marketplace</span> gateway to Ukraine — without Rozetka FBO lock-in</h1>
