    <LabelChip text="03 · COMPARISON" variant="red" />
    <h2 class="rze-h2">Rozetka FBO vs MTP Group vs EU hub (Poland / Czechia)</h2>
    <p class="rz-compare__lead">Honest comparison for international brands entering Ukraine. 12 parameters, no asterisks.</p>
    <div class="rz-compare__scroll">
      <table class="rz-compare__t">
        <thead>
          <tr><th class="rz-compare__th-row">Parameter</th><th>Rozetka FBO</th><th class="rz-compare__th-mtp">MTP Group (UA)</th><th>EU Hub (PL/CZ)</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Categories accepted</td><td><span class="rz-x">×</span> Excludes oversized, glass, cold chain</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> All categories except special</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> Most categories</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Commission on sales</td><td><span class="rz-x">×</span> 4-35% + monthly fee</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> 0% (operations only)</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> 0% (operations only)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Multi-marketplace</td><td><span class="rz-x">×</span> Rozetka only</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> Rozetka + Prom + Kasta + EU + DTC</td><td>Limited Ukraine reach</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Per-shipment cost</td><td>4-35% (variable)</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> €0.40-0.80</td><td>€1.20-2.50</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Pricing currency</td><td>UAH only</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> EUR / USD on request</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> EUR</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Onboarding time</td><td>5-7 business days</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> 2-3 business days</td><td>10-14 business days</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Order SLA</td><td>24 h (norm)</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> 24 min (Rozetka "ideal")</td><td>4-8 h typical</td></tr>
          <tr><td>EU carriers (direct)</td><td><span class="rz-x">×</span> No</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> Nova Post Intl, Meest, DHL, UPS</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> Native</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Insurance coverage</td><td>Up to 50,000 UAH per batch</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> Up to 5M UAH per warehouse</td><td>Standard EU policies</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Brand control</td><td><span class="rz-x">×</span> Rozetka box</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> Your box, inserts, branding</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> Full control</td></tr>
          <tr><td>War resilience (UA market)</td><td>Depends on Rozetka warehouse</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> 3 gens + Starlink + 0 downtime</td><td>Not applicable to UA delivery</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Exit / migration</td><td>Account closure friction</td><td><span class="rz-v">✓</span> 14-day notice, no fees</td><td>Standard 30-day notice</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
    <p class="rz-compare__note">Run your numbers in our <a href="/en/calculator/">calculator</a> — typical EU brand saves 22-38% vs PL/CZ hub for Ukraine GMV.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CATEGORIES WE ACCEPT -->
<section class="rze-cats">
  <div class="rze-cats__inner">
    <LabelChip text="04 · EXCLUDED CATEGORIES" variant="muted" />
    <h2 class="rze-h2">Categories Rozetka FBO refuses, that we accept</h2>
    <div class="rze-cats__grid">
      <article class="rze-cats__card"><h3>Furniture and decor</h3><p>Sofas up to 80 kg, flat-pack wardrobes, tables, beds, chairs, kids furniture, decorative items. Floor-level shelving for oversized goods, lever-pallet handling, separate storage zones. Large-volume pickup from Polish or Hungarian distribution centers.</p></article>
      <article class="rze-cats__card"><h3>Major appliances</h3><p>Refrigerators, washing and dishwashing machines, ovens, air conditioners, freezers. Pre-shipment securing of transport bolts, foam protection, double-walled corrugated boxes. White-glove last-mile delivery via Delivery or partner carriers.</p></article>
      <article class="rze-cats__card"><h3>Fragile glass and mirrors</h3><p>Vases, glassware, decorative pieces, mirrors, glass kitchen surfaces. Multi-layer packaging: air pillows + bubble wrap + corner protectors + double-walled box. Photo verification on dispatch — claims rate under 0.4% across 35,000 shipments in 2024.</p></article>
      <article class="rze-cats__card"><h3>Cosmetics and supplements</h3><p>Decorative cosmetics, skincare, shampoos, supplements at +18…+24°C standard. Separate +2…+8°C cold zone for thermosensitive SKUs with 24/7 temperature monitoring. Cold-chain logs available in dashboard for EU regulatory compliance.</p></article>
      <article class="rze-cats__card"><h3>Electronics and gadgets</h3><p>Smartphones, laptops, tablets, accessories, small appliances, drones. Antistatic packaging, in-box transit fixation, photo capture of serial numbers on each dispatch for brand-protection workflows.</p></article>
      <article class="rze-cats__card"><h3>Children\'s products</h3><p>Toys, strollers, car seats, clothing, baby food. Packaging integrity verification, EN-71 / BSI compliance, +18…+24°C zone for baby food. Documentation handover for Ukrainian retail certification when required.</p></article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

