      <div><h3>Storefronts</h3><ul><li><a href="https://shopify.dev/docs/api" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Shopify (native app)</a></li><li><a href="https://horoshop.ua/ua/api/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Horoshop (native sync)</a></li><li><a href="https://woocommerce.com/document/woocommerce-rest-api/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">WooCommerce (plugin)</a></li><li><a href="https://docs.opencart.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">OpenCart</a>, <a href="https://devdocs.prestashop-project.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">PrestaShop</a></li><li>Custom — webhooks</li></ul></div>
      <div><h3>CRM and ERP</h3><ul><li><a href="https://docs.keycrm.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">KeyCRM</a>, <a href="https://salesdrive.ua/blog/integration/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">SalesDrive</a> (native)</li><li><a href="https://docs.retailcrm.ru/Developers" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">RetailCRM</a>, <a href="https://apidocs.bitrix24.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Bitrix24</a></li><li><a href="https://developers.hubspot.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">HubSpot</a> (via Zapier)</li><li><a href="https://www.odoo.com/documentation/master/developer/reference/external_api.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Odoo</a>, <a href="https://www.amocrm.ru/developers" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">AmoCRM</a></li><li>Custom — REST API</li></ul></div>
